@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_meicqf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.59)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.73 + v2 + 0.53) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.71)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(tmp) - ((v1 + 0.79 - v0 + 0.33) / tmp))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = 0.70
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
